# Title: Hypervisor Enforced Paging Translation Disabled
# Author: Nasreddine Bencherchali (Nextron Systems)
# Date: 2024-07-05
# Level: high
# Description: Detects changes to the "DisableHypervisorEnforcedPagingTranslation" registry value. Where the it is set to "1" in order to disable the Hypervisor Enforced Paging Translation feature.
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.defense-impairment, attack.t1685
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/registry/registry_set/registry_set_deviceguard_hypervisorenforcedpagingtranslation_disabled.yml

Details="DWORD (0x00000001)" TargetObject="*\\DisableHypervisorEnforcedPagingTranslation"